}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== Per the FCC internal photos, this device uses AR9223-AC1A.
The '''TP-LINK''' drivers reference three devices...<small> *168c:002d (168c:0300) **'''TP-LINK 300Mbps Wireless N Adapter''' **This is the PCI ID for the [[TP-LINK TL-WN851ND]]. *168c:002d (168c:0301) **'''TP-LINK 150Mbps Wireless N Adapter''' **This is the PCI ID for the [[TP-LINK TL-WN751ND]]. *168c:0029 (168c:2093) **'''TP-LINK 300Mbps Wireless N Adapter''' **This is the only AR922x (i.e. AR9220 / AR9223) device ID in the drivers. </small>
Possible 90:F6:52 OUI (it is on a label on the back of the device in the FCC photos)
